before the indictment quoted an anonymous investigator as saying 
people were waiting in line to testify against mrs helmsley 
a federal judge who refused to throw out the indictment said 
there was no persuasive evidence that the grand jury was influenced 
by the news coverage 
the case is helmsley vs us 88732 
