national science scholars program 
in a draft message to congress circulating along with the bill 
bush said the plan rewards excellence directs federal dollars to 
those most in need gives parents and school systems greater 
flexibility and choice and increases accountability by measuring 
and rewarding progress toward quality education 
congressional response to bushs proposals has been mixed 
several lawmakers including house education and labor committee 
