system 
the defendants lawyers said they had done nothing wrong 
the three former teledyne electronics executives george kaub 
dale schnittjer and eugene sullivan are charged with bribery 
conspiracy and making false statements in an indictment handed up 
by the grand jury three months ago 
all worked for the newbury park calif company that is a 
subsidiary of teledyne ndustries which has already pleaded guilty 
in the case in addition a former navy procurement official and 
