robert wise is the wonder of the movie 
season a 74yearold oscar winner who has directed an 
actionfilled tightly budgeted movie on the mean streets of 
manhattans lower east side 
rooftops has proved less than a wonder with critics and at 
the box office but reviewers have generally praised wises 
