the backgrounds of lower east side in fine style 
born in westchester ind robert wise came west to enter the 
movie business and landed a job in the editing department of rko in 
1933 his editing of citizen kane won his first academy award 
nomination in 1940 after serving his apprenticeship as director 
he became known as a man who could deal with varied temperaments 
and complex productions 
wise has been laden with honors including oscars for the 
