berlioz 18031832 the making of an artist at the university in 
davis where he spent two terms as a visiting professor 
kern holoman chairman of the music department there arranged 
it and it meant i was free from journalism hes one of the worlds 
leading berlioz scholars and is writing a lifeandworks of the 
composer the author said 
asked why he got such help on what might be seen as a rival 
