surgeon generals report said f edward scarbrough deputy 
director of the fdas office of nutrition and food sciences center 
of food safety and applied nutrition 
five things would be addressed fats and heart disease fats and 
cancer fiber and cancer calcium and osteoporosis and sodium and 
hypertension the fda would come up with model label statements 
